        <Parent_String>linear distance measuring devices [300198750], distance measuring devices [300195705], measuring devices for extent [300195701], measuring devices (instruments) [300207870], Measuring Devices (hierarchy name) [300207851], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Straight poles graduated with numerical and geometric marks that are held upright and used with transits or other surveying instruments equipped with stadia hairs to measure horizontal distances. For similar poles graduated with numerical marks for measuring heights or elevations, use "leveling rods."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Úsese para para varas rectas y graduadas con marcas numéricas y geométricas que se sostienen en forma vertical y se usan con teodolitos u otros instrumentos de agrimensura equipados con dos líneas paralelas ("stadia hairs”) para medir distancias horizontales. Para varas similares graduadas con marcas numéricas para medir alturas o elevaciones, use "vara de nivelación.”</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wordt gebruikt voor rechte stokken met een schaalverdeling in numerieke en geometrische tekens, die rechtop worden gehouden en worden gebruikt met transietinstrumenten of andere landmeetkundige instrumenten die zijn uitgerust met horizontale kruisharen voor het meten van horizontale afstanden. Gebruik 'niveaulatten' voor soortgelijke palen met een numerieke onderverdelingen voor het meten van hoogtes en verhogingen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052381/Van Dale Engels-Nederlands (1989)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>筆直的杆子，上面標示著數字和幾何記號，使用時垂直置放，並配合子午儀或其他有視距絲裝置的量測儀器，用於測量水平的距離；而構造相似、刻有數字記號，用來測量高度或上升高度的杆子，則稱「水準尺」。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052784/TELDAP database (2009-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Gerader Stab mit numerischen und geometrischen Skalenmarkierungen, der senkrecht gehalten und zusammen mit Theodoliten oder anderen mit Fadenkreuzen ausgerüsteten Vermessungsinstrumenten zur Messung horizontaler Abstände verwendet wird. Für einen ähnlichen Stab mit numerischen Markierungen zum Messen von Höhen oder Erhebungen, siehe "Nivellierlatte".</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000122134/IfM Berlin</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
